      "topic": "brief",
      "sender": "User",
      "content": "\nCreate a responsive and visually appealing TODO list widget for a website. Users should be able to add tasks, mark tasks as complete, and delete tasks. Include features such as task prioritization, due dates, and categorization. \n\nYou may also add any additional creative features to enhance usability and enjoyment, such as notifications or task exporting. \n\nUse only HTML, CSS, and JavaScript — do not use Vue, React, or any third-party libraries. Store all data using localStorage, ensuring tasks persist after page refresh. Keep the overall design simple, user-friendly, and engaging.\n\n"
    }
  ],
